{"tid":252954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"研究：Instagram最損害青少年精神健康　","createTime":"2017-05-22T03:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T03:22:07.000Z","uid":68813,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce04472265c11f899351f5010f47aa847a18e1c","tid":252954,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T03:48:21.000Z","msg":"英國皇家公共衛生學會一項研究發現，Instagram是最損害青少年精神健康的社交平台，指它會加深他們焦慮、抑鬱等負面感覺。<br />\n其他報道：日本內閣通過天皇退位法案　容許明仁退位<br />\n皇家公共衛生學會訪問了1479名14至24歲的年輕網民，調查YouTube、Twitter、facebook、Instagram和Snapchat 5個社交平台，對他們的身心健康有何負面影響，受訪者須回答14條問題，就每個平台有關焦慮、抑鬱、孤獨、欺凌及身材等問題逐一評分。<br />\n結果顯示，YouTube被青少年評為對精神健康產生最正面的影響，其次是Twitter和facebook，Snapchat和Instagram的評分就最低，被認為最不利精神健康的社交平台。<br />\n皇家公共衛生學會總裁克拉默（Shirley Cramer）指出，評分最低的Snapchat和Instagram都是以分享照片為主，這可能是推動年輕人缺乏信心和焦慮的原因所在。<br />\n20多歲的英國女子伊絲拉（Isla）是其中一個案例，她承認，自己多年來沉迷上社交網，在網上世界感到受重視，但後來覺得自己開始忽略真實生活中的友誼，並因此陷入嚴重抑鬱。她說：「那時候，覺得社交媒體令我感覺很差，因我不停拿自己跟別人比較&hellip;&hellip;當看到朋友發佈自己所做的事時，我會憎恨自己為何不能像他們一樣，又或為何不能和別人一樣好。」<br />\n專家認為，社交媒體公司應設法協助網民解決精神健康問題，如彈出警告，提醒用家勿長時間使用社交平台，又或識別出一些有精神健康問題的用戶，提醒他們在哪裏可獲支援。<br />\n（英國廣播公司）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170519/s00005/1495200459034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170519%2Fs00005%2F1495200459034&d=oSiF6q%2BHtSOEBVfNLUnrLP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=841a81d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170519%2Fs00005%2F1495200459034&h=7576e1f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170519/s00005/1495200459034</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">之前見到呢個POST，<br />\n<br />\n都聽過朋友講通常係FB 係PO曬命開心野，IG就係PO D 唔開心野，有無人都係咁架？</span></span>"},{"pid":"a31f22e1d899bf186b277d9dc85af419ec262847","tid":252954,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"youtube 係撚社交平台"},{"pid":"f7b995033e06136270c32a95502738f10e9fc2ed","tid":252954,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"ig = online game"},{"pid":"c93794a6bb97392786a5dd68f224aa7e9543ea02","tid":252954,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ig = online game</blockquote><br />\n姐係？"},{"pid":"82c70185f88dbb71dda14c247a909df9c1a5ed8c","tid":252954,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:33:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>youtube 係撚社交平台</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  正解!!!<br />\n不過可能講緊D青少年喜歡LOR"},{"pid":"6eb70ec5d0c3e52548da81d6c4eafde936c6d9a1","tid":252954,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>youtube 係撚社交平台</blockquote><br />\n以前嘅youtube算係嘅,同ig差唔多"},{"pid":"a7ad2baac6f6cda90d397cf1fd64106d1fa94993","tid":252954,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>youtube 係撚社交平台</blockquote><br />\n以前嘅youtube算係嘅,同ig差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過，認真，大家係咪成日都玩youtube？我指係好似IG / FB咁 share好多自己野？"},{"pid":"ab2ddcf3033e4db40464b0ebe39de4eeb1d16f75","tid":252954,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>youtube 係撚社交平台</blockquote><br />\n以前嘅youtube算係嘅,同ig差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過，認真，大家係咪成日都玩youtube？我指係好似IG / FB咁 share好多自己野？</blockquote><br />\nYouTube 用黎睇片學下野<br />\n又可以娛樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /